lead_paragraph: The Australian Olympic team refused to move in to Rio de Janeiro's village for athletes on Sunday, saying the accommodation was "not safe or ready" for next month's games.

headline.print_headline: Australians Stay Away From Village Citing Blocked Toilets, Exposed Wiring
